#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:656
msgid "`freebsd-boot` - Holds the FreeBSD boot code."
msgstr "`freebsd-boot` - 存放 FreeBSD 的启动代码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:657
msgid "`freebsd-ufs` - A FreeBSD UFS file system."
msgstr "`freebsd-ufs` - 一个 FreeBSD UFS 文件系统。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:658
msgid "`freebsd-zfs` - A FreeBSD ZFS file system. More information about ZFS is available in crossref:zfs[zfs,The Z File System (ZFS)]."
msgstr "`freebsd-zfs` - 一个 FreeBSD ZFS 文件系统。关于 ZFS 的更多信息可以在 Z 文件系统（ZFS）中找到。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:659
msgid "`freebsd-swap` - FreeBSD swap space."
msgstr "`freebsd-swap` - FreeBSD 交换空间。"

#. type: Plain text
