"file systems on their own partitions, create a GPT partitioning scheme, then create the partitions as shown.  Partition sizes shown are typical "
"for a 20G target disk.  If more space is available on the target disk, larger swap or [.filename]#/var# partitions may be useful.  Labels shown "
