"After the custom partitions have been created, select btn:[Finish] to continue with the installation and go to <<bsdinstall-fetching-"
"distribution>>."
msgstr "自定义分区创建完毕后，选择btn:[Finish] 继续安装，并进入 <<bsdinstall-fetching-distribution>>。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:744
#, no-wrap
msgid "Guided Partitioning Using Root-on-ZFS"
msgstr "使用 Root-on-ZFS 进行向导式分区"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:748
msgid ""
"This partitioning mode only works with whole disks and will erase the contents of the entire disk.  The main ZFS configuration menu offers a "
"number of options to control the creation of the pool."
msgstr "这种分区模式只适用于整个磁盘，并且会擦除整个磁盘的内容。ZFS 的主配置菜单提供了许多选项来控制池的创建。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:750
#, no-wrap
msgid "ZFS Partitioning Menu"
msgstr "ZFS 分区选项"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:751
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-menu.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-menu.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:754
msgid "Here is a summary of the options which can be used in this menu:"
msgstr "下面是这个菜单中可以使用的选项的摘要介绍："

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:756
msgid "`Install` - Proceed with the installation with the selected options."
msgstr "`Install` - 使用选定的选项继续安装。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:757
msgid ""
"`Pool Type/Disks` - Allow to configure the `Pool Type` and the disk(s) that will constitute the pool. The automatic ZFS installer currently only "
"supports the creation of a single top level vdev, except in stripe mode. To create more complex pools, use the instructions in <<bsdinstall-part-"
"shell>> to create the pool."
msgstr ""
"`Pool Type/Disks` - 允许配置池类型和将构成池的磁盘。自动 ZFS 安装程序目前只支持创建一个顶层的vdev，除了在 stripe 模式下。要创建更复杂的池，请使用 "
"<<bsdinstall-part-shell>> 中的说明来创建池。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:758
msgid "`Rescan Devices` - Repopulate the list of available disks."
msgstr "`Rescan Devices` - 重新填充可用磁盘的列表。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:759
msgid ""
"`Disk Info` - Disk Info menu can be used to inspect each disk, including its partition table and various other information such as the device "
"model number and serial number, if available."
msgstr "`Disk Info` - 磁盘信息菜单可以用来检查每个磁盘，包括它的分区表和其他各种信息，如设备型号和序列号（如果有）。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:760
msgid "`Pool Name` - Establish the name of the pool. The default name is _zroot_."
msgstr "`Pool Name` - 建立磁盘池的名称。默认名称是_zroot_。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:761
msgid ""
"`Force 4K Sectors?` - Force the use of 4K sectors. By default, the installer will automatically create partitions aligned to 4K boundaries and "
"force ZFS to use 4K sectors. This is safe even with 512 byte sector disks, and has the added benefit of ensuring that pools created on 512 byte "
"disks will be able to have 4K sector disks added in the future, either as additional storage space or as replacements for failed disks. Press the "
"kbd:[Enter] key to chose to activate it or not."
msgstr ""
"`Force 4K Sectors?` - 强制使用 4K 扇区。默认情况下，安装程序会自动创建与 4K 边界对齐的分区并强制 ZFS 使用 4K 扇区。这在 512 字节扇区的磁盘上也是安"
"全的，而且还有一个额外的好处，那就是确保在 512 字节磁盘上创建的池子将来可以添加 4K 扇区的磁盘，作为额外的存储空间或替换故障磁盘。按回车键kbd:"
"[Enter]，选择是否激活它。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:762
msgid ""
"`Encrypt Disks?` - Encrypting the disks allows the user to encrypt the disks using GELI. More information about disk encryption is available in "
"crossref:disks[disks-encrypting-geli,“Disk Encryption with geli”]. Press the kbd:[Enter] key to chose activate it or not."
msgstr ""
"`Encrypt Disks?` - 加密磁盘允许用户使用 GELI 对磁盘进行加密。更多关于磁盘加密的信息可以在 crossref:disks[disks-encrypting-geli,“Disk Encryption "
"with geli”] 中找到。按回车键kbd:[Enter] ，选择是否激活它。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:763
msgid ""
"`Partition Scheme` - Allow to choose the partition scheme. GPT is the recommended option in most cases. Press the kbd:[Enter] key to chose "
"between the different options."
msgstr "`Partition Scheme` - 允许选择分区方案。GPT 是大多数情况下的推荐选项。按回车键在不同的选项中进行选择。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:764
msgid "`Swap Size` - Establish the amount of swap space."
msgstr "`Swap Size` - 建立交换空间的数量。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:765
msgid ""
"`Mirror Swap?` - Allows the user to mirror the swap between the disks. Be aware, enabling mirror swap will break crash dumps. Press the kbd:"
"[Enter] key to activate it or not."
msgstr "`Mirror Swap?` - 允许用户在磁盘之间做镜像交换。请注意，启用镜像交换将破坏崩溃转储。按回车键来激活或不激活。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:766
msgid ""
"`Encrypt Swap?` - Allow the user the possibility to encrypt the swap. Encrypts the swap with a temporary key each time that the system boots and "
"discards it on reboot. Press the kbd:[Enter] key to chose activate it or not. More information about swap encryption in crossref:disks[swap-"
"encrypting,“Encrypting Swap”]."
msgstr ""
"`Encrypt Swap?` - 允许用户对交换盘进行加密。每次系统启动时，用一个临时密钥加密交换，并在重启时丢弃。按回车键可以选择是否激活它。在crossref:"
"disks[swap-encrypting,“加密 Swap”]中有更多关于交换分区加密的信息。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:768
msgid "Select kbd:[T] to configure the `Pool Type` and the disk(s) that will constitute the pool."
msgstr "选择 kbd:[T] 来配置`Pool Type` 和构成池的磁盘。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:770
#, no-wrap
msgid "ZFS Pool Type"
msgstr "ZFS 池类型"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:771
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-vdev_type.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-vdev_type.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:774
msgid "Here is a summary of the `Pool Type` which can be selected in this menu:"
msgstr "下面是在这个菜单中可以选择的Pool Type的摘要："

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:776
msgid ""
"`stripe` - Striping provides maximum storage of all connected devices, but no redundancy. If just one disk fails the data on the pool is lost "
"irrevocably."
msgstr "`stripe` - 条带化提供所有连接设备的最大存储量，但没有冗余。如果只有一个磁盘发生故障，池上的数据将不可逆转地丢失。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:777
msgid ""
"`mirror` - Mirroring stores a complete copy of all data on every disk. Mirroring provides a good read performance because data is read from all "
"disks in parallel. Write performance is slower as the data must be written to all disks in the pool. Allows all but one disk to fail. This option "
"requires at least two disks."
msgstr ""
"`mirror` - 镜像在每个磁盘上存储所有数据的一个完整副本。镜像提供了良好的读取性能，因为数据是从所有磁盘上平行读取的。写入性能较慢，因为数据必须写到"
"池中的所有磁盘上。允许除一个磁盘外的所有磁盘发生故障。这个选项至少需要两个磁盘。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:778
msgid ""
"`raid10` - Striped mirrors. Provides the best performance, but the least storage. This option needs at least an even number of disks and a "
"minimum of four disks."
msgstr "`raid10` - 带状镜像。提供最好的性能，但存储量最少。这个选项至少需要偶数个磁盘，至少需要四个磁盘。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:779
msgid "`raidz1` - Single Redundant RAID. Allow one disk to fail concurrently. This option needs at least three disks."
msgstr "`raidz1` - 单一冗余 RAID。允许一个磁盘同时发生故障。该选项至少需要 3 个磁盘。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:780
msgid "`raidz2` - Double Redundant RAID. Allows two disks to fail concurrently. This option needs at least four disks."
msgstr "`raidz2` - 双重冗余 RAID。允许两个磁盘同时发生故障。该选项至少需要 4 个磁盘。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:781
msgid "`raidz3` - Triple Redundant RAID. Allows three disks to fail concurrently. This option needs at least five disks."
msgstr "`raidz3` - 三重冗余 RAID。允许三个磁盘同时发生故障。该选项至少需要 5 个磁盘。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:785
msgid ""
"Once a `Pool Type` has been selected, a list of available disks is displayed, and the user is prompted to select one or more disks to make up the "
"pool.  The configuration is then validated, to ensure enough disks are selected.  If not, select btn:[<Change Selection>] to return to the list "
"of disks, or btn:[<Back>] to change the `Pool Type`."
msgstr ""
"选择了 `Pool Type` 之后，就会显示可用的磁盘列表，并提示用户选择一个或多个磁盘来组成池。然后，配置会被验证，以确保有足够的磁盘被选中。如果没有，选"
"择btn:[<Change Selection>] 回到磁盘列表，或者 btn:[<Back>] 改变池类型。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:787
#, no-wrap
msgid "Disk Selection"
msgstr "选择硬盘"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:788
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-disk_select.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-disk_select.png"

