#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:795
msgid ""
"If one or more disks are missing from the list, or if disks were attached after the installer was started, select btn:[- Rescan Devices] to "
"repopulate the list of available disks."
msgstr "如果列表中缺少一个或多个磁盘，或者磁盘是在安装程序启动后连接的，请选择——btn:[- Rescan Devices] 设备来重新填充可用磁盘的列表。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:797
#, no-wrap
msgid "Rescan Devices"
msgstr "重新扫描硬盘"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:798
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-rescan-devices.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-rescan-devices.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:801
msgid ""
"To avoid accidentally erasing the wrong disk, the btn:[- Disk Info] menu can be used to inspect each disk, including its partition table and "
"various other information such as the device model number and serial number, if available."
msgstr "为了避免意外地擦除错误的磁盘， btn:[- Disk Info] 菜单可以用来检查每个磁盘，包括其分区表和其他各种信息，如设备型号和序列号（如果有的话）。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:803
#, no-wrap
msgid "Analyzing a Disk"
msgstr "分析硬盘"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:804
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-disk_info.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-disk_info.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:808
msgid ""
"Select kbd:[N] to configure the `Pool Name`.  Enter the desired name then select btn:[<OK>] to establish it or btn:[<Cancel>] to return to the "
"main menu and leave the default name."
msgstr "选择 kbd:[N] 来配置`Pool Name`。输入所需的名称，然后选择btn:[<OK>] 建立它，或 btn:[<Cancel>] 返回主菜单并保留默认名称。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:810
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pool Name"
msgstr "存储池名"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:811
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-pool-name.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-pool-name.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:815
msgid ""
"Select kbd:[S] to set the amount of swap.  Enter the desired amount of swap and then select btn:[<OK>] to establish it or btn:[<Cancel>] to "
"return to the main menu and let the default amount."
msgstr "选择 kbd:[S] 来设置交换量。输入所需的交换量，然后选择btn:[<OK>]建立，或选择btn:[<Cancel>]返回主菜单，让其使用默认量。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:817
#, no-wrap
msgid "Swap Amount"
msgstr "交换量"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:818
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-swap-amount.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-swap-amount.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:822
msgid ""
"Once all options have been set to the desired values, select the btn:[>>> Install] option at the top of the menu.  The installer then offers a "
"last chance to cancel before the contents of the selected drives are destroyed to create the ZFS pool."
msgstr ""
"所有的选项都被设置为所需的值之后，选择菜单顶部的btn:[>>> Install] 。然后安装程序提供了一个最后的机会，在所选驱动器的内容被销毁以创建 ZFS 池之前，"
"可以取消。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:824
#, no-wrap
msgid "Last Chance"
msgstr "最后的机会"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:825
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-warning.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-warning.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:829
msgid ""
"If GELI disk encryption was enabled, the installer will prompt twice for the passphrase to be used to encrypt the disks.  And after that the "
"initializing of the encryption begins."
msgstr "如果启用了 GELI 磁盘加密，安装程序将提示两次用于加密磁盘的口令。而后开始初始化加密。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:831
#, no-wrap
msgid "Disk Encryption Password"
msgstr "硬盘加密密码"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:832
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-geli_password.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-geli_password.png"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:835
#, no-wrap
msgid "Initializing Encryption"
msgstr "初始化加密"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:836
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-zfs-init-encription.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-zfs-init-encription.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:840
msgid "The installation then proceeds normally.  To continue with the installation go to <<bsdinstall-fetching-distribution>>."
msgstr "然后安装会正常进行。要继续安装，请进入<<bsdinstall-fetching-distribution>>。"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:842
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shell Mode Partitioning"
msgstr "SHELL 模式分区"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:847
msgid ""
"When creating advanced installations, the bsdinstall partitioning menus may not provide the level of flexibility required.  Advanced users can "
"select the btn:[Shell] option from the partitioning menu in order to manually partition the drives, create the file system(s), populate [."
"filename]#/tmp/bsdinstall_etc/fstab#, and mount the file systems under [.filename]#/mnt#.  Once this is done, type `exit` to return to bsdinstall "
"and continue the installation."
msgstr ""
"在创建高级安装时，bsdinstall 的分区菜单可能无法提供所需的灵活性水平。高级用户可以从分区菜单中选择 btn:[Shell] 选项，以便手动对驱动器进行分区，创建"
"文件系统，填充 [.filename]#/tmp/bsdinstall_etc/fstab#，并在 [.filename]#/mnt# 下加载文件系统。完成后，键入`exit`，返回bsdinstall，继续安装。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:849 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:858
#, no-wrap
msgid "Fetching Distribution Files"
msgstr "获取安装文件"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:853
msgid ""
"Installation time will vary depending on the distributions chosen, installation media, and speed of the computer.  A series of messages will "
"indicate the progress."
msgstr "安装时间将取决于所选择的组件、安装媒体和计算机的速度。一系列的信息都将显示进度。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:856
msgid ""
"First, the installer formats the selected disk(s) and initializes the partitions.  Next, in the case of a `bootonly media` or `mini memstick`, it "
"downloads the selected components:"
msgstr "首先，安装程序会格式化所选磁盘并初始化分区。接下来，如果是`bootonly media`或`mini memstick`，它会下载所选的组件："

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:859
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-distfile-fetching.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-distfile-fetching.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:862
msgid ""
"Next, the integrity of the distribution files is verified to ensure they have not been corrupted during download or misread from the installation "
"media:"
msgstr "接下来，分发文件的完整性得到验证，以确保它们在下载过程中没有被破坏或从安装介质中误读："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:864
#, no-wrap
msgid "Verifying Distribution Files"
msgstr "校验发行文件"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:865
#, no-wrap
