msgstr "bsdinstall-distfile-verifying.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:868
msgid "Finally, the verified distribution files are extracted to the disk:"
msgstr "最后，经过验证的发行文件被提取到磁盘："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:870
#, no-wrap
msgid "Extracting Distribution Files"
msgstr "解压缩发行文件"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:871
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-distfile-extracting.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-distfile-extracting.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:875
msgid ""
"Once all requested distribution files have been extracted, bsdinstall displays the first post-installation configuration screen.  The available "
"post-configuration options are described in the next section."
msgstr "如果所有要求的发行文件都被解压缩，bsdinstall会显示第一个安装后配置屏幕。可用的后配置选项将在下一节描述。"

#. type: Title ==
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:877
#, no-wrap
msgid "Accounts, Time Zone, Services and Hardening"
msgstr "账户、时区、服务和安全"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:880 content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:888
#, no-wrap
msgid "Setting the `root` Password"
msgstr "设置`root`密码"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:886
msgid ""
"First, the `root` password must be set.  While entering the password, the characters being typed are not displayed on the screen.  After the "
"password has been entered, it must be entered again.  This helps prevent typing errors."
msgstr "首先，必须设置root密码。在输入密码时，正在输入的字符不会显示在屏幕上。输入密码后，必须再次输入。这有助于防止输入错误。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:889
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-post-root-passwd.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-post-root-passwd.png"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:892
#, no-wrap
msgid "Setting the Time Zone"
msgstr "设置时区"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:896
msgid ""
"The next series of menus are used to determine the correct local time by selecting the geographic region, country, and time zone.  Setting the "
"time zone allows the system to automatically correct for regional time changes, such as daylight savings time, and perform other time zone "
"related functions properly."
msgstr ""
