msgstr "`System Hardening` - 在 <<bsdinstall-hardening>>中描述。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1054
msgid "`Time Zone` - Described in <<bsdinstall-timezone>>."
msgstr "`Time Zone` - 在<<bsdinstall-timezone>>中进行了描述。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1055
msgid "`Handbook` - Download and install the FreeBSD Handbook."
msgstr "`Handbook` - 下载并安装 FreeBSD 手册。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1057
msgid "After any final configuration is complete, select btn:[Exit]."
msgstr "在任何最终配置完成后，选择 btn:[Exit]。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1059
#, no-wrap
msgid "Manual Configuration"
msgstr "手动设置"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1060
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-final-modification-shell.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-final-modification-shell.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1064
msgid ""
"bsdinstall will prompt if there are any additional configuration that needs to be done before rebooting into the new system.  Select btn:[Yes] to "
"exit to a shell within the new system or btn:[No] to proceed to the last step of the installation."
msgstr "bsdinstall 会提示在重启到新系统之前是否有任何其他配置需要完成。选择btn:[Yes] 退出到新系统的 shell，或者选择 btn:[No] 进入安装的最后一步。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1066
#, no-wrap
msgid "Complete the Installation"
msgstr "完成安装"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1067
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-mainexit.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-mainexit.png"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1070
msgid "If further configuration or special setup is needed, select btn:[Live CD] to boot the install media into Live CD mode."
msgstr "如果需要进一步的配置或特殊的设置，选择 btn:[Live CD] 来启动安装介质进入 Live CD 模式。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1073
msgid ""
"If the installation is complete, select btn:[Reboot] to reboot the computer and start the new FreeBSD system.  Do not forget to remove the "
"FreeBSD install media or the computer may boot from it again."
msgstr "如果安装完成，选择 btn:[Reboot] 来重新启动计算机并开始新的 FreeBSD 系统。不要忘记卸载 FreeBSD 的安装介质，否则计算机可能会再次从它启动。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1079
msgid ""
"As FreeBSD boots, informational messages are displayed.  After the system finishes booting, a login prompt is displayed.  At the `login:` prompt, "
"enter the username added during the installation.  Avoid logging in as `root`.  Refer to crossref:basics[users-superuser,“The Superuser Account”] "
"for instructions on how to become the superuser when administrative access is needed."
msgstr ""
"当 FreeBSD 启动时，会显示一些信息性的信息。在系统完成启动后，会显示一个登录提示。在 `login:` 的提示下，输入安装时添加的用户名。避免以 `root` 身份"
"登录。了解在需要管理权限时如何成为超级用户的说明，请参考crossref:basics[users-superuser,“The Superuser Account”] 。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1085
msgid ""
"The messages that appeared during boot can be reviewed by pressing kbd:[Scroll-Lock] to turn on the scroll-back buffer.  The kbd:[PgUp], kbd:"
"[PgDn], and arrow keys can be used to scroll back through the messages.  When finished, press kbd:[Scroll-Lock] again to unlock the display and "
"return to the console.  To review these messages once the system has been up for some time, type `less /var/run/dmesg.boot` from a command "
"prompt.  Press kbd:[q] to return to the command line after viewing."
msgstr ""
"按kbd:[Scroll-Lock] 打开回卷缓冲器，就可以查看启动时出现的信息。可以用 kbd:[PgUp]、kbd:[PgDn] 和方向键来回滚信息。完成后，再按一次 kbd:[Scroll-"
"Lock] 键，解除显示并返回到控制台。要在系统运行一段时间后查看这些信息，可以在命令提示符下输入`less /var/run/dmesg.boot`。查看后按 kbd:[q] 键返回到"
"命令行。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
