#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1130
msgid "Refer to crossref:security[openssh,\"OpenSSH\"] for more information about fingerprints and SSH."
msgstr "关于指纹和 SSH 的更多信息请参考 crossref:security[openssh,”OpenSSH”]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1133
msgid ""
"FreeBSD does not install a graphical environment by default.  Refer to crossref:x11[x11,The X Window System] for more information about "
"installing and configuring a graphical window manager."
msgstr "FreeBSD 默认不会安装图形环境。请参考 crossref:x11[x11,The X Window 系统] 以了解更多关于安装和配置图形化窗口管理器的信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1137
msgid ""
"Proper shutdown of a FreeBSD computer helps protect data and hardware from damage.  _Do not turn off the power before the system has been "
"properly shut down!_ If the user is a member of the `wheel` group, become the superuser by typing `su` at the command line and entering the "
"`root` password.  Then, type `shutdown -p now` and the system will shut down cleanly, and if the hardware supports it, turn itself off."
msgstr ""
"正确地关闭 FreeBSD 计算机有助于保护数据和硬件免受损害。_在系统正确关闭之前，请不要关闭电源！_如果用户是 `wheel` 组的成员，通过在命令行输入 `su` 并"
"输入 `root` 密码，成为超级用户。然后，输入`shutdown -p now`，系统就会干净利落地关闭，如果硬件支持，就会自动关闭。"

#. type: Title ==
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1139
#, no-wrap
msgid "Network Interfaces"
msgstr "网络接口"

#. type: Title ===
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1142
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuring Network Interfaces"
msgstr "配置网络接口"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1146
msgid "Next, a list of the network interfaces found on the computer is shown.  Select the interface to configure."
msgstr "接下来，会显示计算机上发现的网络接口的列表。选择要配置的接口。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1148
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose a Network Interface"
msgstr "选择网络接口"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1149
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1153
msgid ""
"If an Ethernet interface is selected, the installer will skip ahead to the menu shown in <<bsdinstall-configure-net-ipv4>>.  If a wireless "
"network interface is chosen, the system will instead scan for wireless access points:"
msgstr "如果选择了以太网接口，安装程序将跳到 <<bsdinstall-configure-net-ipv4>>中显示的菜单。如果选择了无线网络接口，系统将转而扫描无线接入点："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1155
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scanning for Wireless Access Points"
msgstr "正在扫描接入点"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1156
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-scan.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-scan.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1163
msgid ""
"Wireless networks are identified by a Service Set Identifier (SSID), a short, unique name given to each network.  SSIDs found during the scan are "
"listed, followed by a description of the encryption types available for that network.  If the desired SSID does not appear in the list, select "
"btn:[Rescan] to scan again.  If the desired network still does not appear, check for problems with antenna connections or try moving the computer "
"closer to the access point.  Rescan after each change is made."
msgstr ""
"无线网络是由服务集标识符（SSID）来识别的，这是给予每个网络的一个简短而独特的名称。在扫描过程中发现的 SSID 会被列出，然后是对该网络可用的加密类型的"
"描述。如果所需的 SSID 没有出现在列表中，选择btn:[Rescan] 以再次扫描。如果想要的网络仍然没有出现，请检查天线连接是否有问题，或者尝试将电脑移到离接"
"入点更近的地方。每次改变后都要重新扫描。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1165
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choosing a Wireless Network"
msgstr "选择无线网络"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1166
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-accesspoints.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-accesspoints.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1172
msgid ""
"Next, enter the encryption information for connecting to the selected wireless network.  WPA2 encryption is strongly recommended as older "
"encryption types, like WEP, offer little security.  If the network uses WPA2, input the password, also known as the Pre-Shared Key (PSK).  For "
"security reasons, the characters typed into the input box are displayed as asterisks."
msgstr ""
"接下来，输入连接到所选无线网络的加密信息。强烈建议使用 WPA2 加密，因为旧的加密类型，如 WEP，提供的安全性不高。如果网络使用 WPA2，请输入密码，也被"
"称为预共享密钥（PSK）。出于安全考虑，输入框中的字符会显示为星号。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1174
#, no-wrap
msgid "WPA2 Setup"
msgstr "设置 WPA2"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1175
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-wpa2setup.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-wireless-wpa2setup.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1178
msgid "Next, choose whether or not an IPv4 address should be configured on the Ethernet or wireless interface:"
msgstr "接下来，选择是否要在以太网或无线接口上配置一个 IPv4 地址："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1180
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose IPv4 Networking"
msgstr "选择 IPv4 地址"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1181
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1186
msgid ""
"There are two methods of IPv4 configuration.  DHCP will automatically configure the network interface correctly and should be used if the network "
"provides a DHCP server.  Otherwise, the addressing information needs to be input manually as a static configuration."
msgstr ""
"有两种配置 IPv4 的方法。DHCP 会自动正确配置网络接口，如果网络提供了 DHCP 服务器，就应该使用这种方法。否则，寻址信息需要以静态配置的方式手动输入。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1191
msgid ""
"Do not enter random network information as it will not work.  If a DHCP server is not available, obtain the information listed in <<bsdinstall-"
"collect-network-information, Required Network Information>> from the network administrator or Internet service provider."
msgstr ""
"不要随意输入网络信息，因为它将无法工作。如果没有 DHCP 服务器，请从网络管理员或互联网服务提供商那里获得<<bsdinstall-collect-network-information, 所"
"需网络信息>> 中列出的信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1195
msgid ""
"If a DHCP server is available, select btn:[Yes] in the next menu to automatically configure the network interface.  The installer will appear to "
"pause for a minute or so as it finds the DHCP server and obtains the addressing information for the system."
msgstr "如果有 DHCP 服务器，在下一个菜单中选择 Yes来自动配置网络接口。当安装程序找到 DHCP 服务器并获得系统的寻址信息时，会出现一分钟左右的停顿。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1197
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose IPv4DHCP Configuration"
msgstr "选择 IPv4 DHCP 配置"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1198
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4-dhcp.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4-dhcp.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1201
msgid "If a DHCP server is not available, select btn:[No] and input the following addressing information in this menu:"
msgstr "如果没有 DHCP 服务器，请选择 btn:[No]，并在此菜单中输入以下寻址信息："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1203
#, no-wrap
msgid "IPv4 Static Configuration"
msgstr "IPv4 静态配置"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1204
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4-static.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv4-static.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1207
msgid ""
"`IP Address` - The IPv4 address assigned to this computer. The address must be unique and not already in use by another piece of equipment on the "
"local network."
msgstr "`IP Address` - 分配给该计算机的 IPv4 地址。该地址必须是唯一的，并且没有被本地网络中的其他设备使用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1208
msgid "`Subnet Mask` - The subnet mask for the network."
msgstr "`Subnet Mask` - 网络的子网掩码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1209
msgid "`Default Router` - The IP address of the network's default gateway."
msgstr "`Default Router` - 网络的默认网关的 IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1211
msgid "The next screen will ask if the interface should be configured for IPv6. If IPv6 is available and desired, choose btn:[Yes] to select it."
msgstr "下一个屏幕将询问该接口是否应配置为 IPv6。如果 IPv6 可用并且需要，请选择 btn:[Yes] 来选择它。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1213
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose IPv6 Networking"
msgstr "选择 IPv6 网络"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1214
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv6.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-ipv6.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1220
msgid ""
"IPv6 also has two methods of configuration.  StateLess Address AutoConfiguration (SLAAC) will automatically request the correct configuration "
"information from a local router.  Refer to http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4862[rfc4862] for more information.  Static configuration requires "
"manual entry of network information."
msgstr ""
"IPv6 也有两种配置方法。无状态地址自动配置（SLAAC）将自动向本地路由器请求正确的配置信息。更多信息请参考 http://tools.ietf.org/html/"
"rfc4862[rfc4862]。静态配置需要手动输入网络信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1223
msgid ""
"If an IPv6 router is available, select btn:[Yes] in the next menu to automatically configure the network interface.  The installer will appear to "
"pause for a minute or so as it finds the router and obtains the addressing information for the system."
msgstr "如果有 IPv6 路由器，请在下一个菜单中选择btn:[Yes]，以自动配置网络接口。安装程序在找到路由器并获得系统的寻址信息时，会出现一分钟左右的停顿。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose IPv6 SLAAC Configuration"
msgstr "选择 IPv6 SLAAC 配置"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1226
#, no-wrap
msgid "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-slaac.png"
msgstr "bsdinstall-configure-network-interface-slaac.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1229
msgid "If an IPv6 router is not available, select btn:[No] and input the following addressing information in this menu:"
msgstr "如果没有 IPv6 路由器，请选择btn:[No] 并在该菜单中输入以下寻址信息："

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:1231
